(97, '2', 'announcement', 0, 'Byunghoon Yoon', 'Korean Community Fall Forum 2011', '<div style="text-align:center;"><b>Korean Community Fall Forum 2011: Understanding Our Community and Higher Education</b></div><div>I am pleased to invite you to the Korean Community Fall Forum 2011. This is jointly organized by the Toronto Korean Families Study(TKFS) and the Korean-Canadian University Professors Forum(KCUPF).</div><div>This Forum''s aims are threefold: 1)to inform both parents and students who are senior high school or university students about the life of a post-secondary school student; 2)to provide an opportunity for them to meet university professors and current university students for potential networking; 3) it will be the first time t present the results of the TKFS project and to thank publicly the Korean community who supported us.</div><div><br /></div><div>Please find details in the attached file. I thank you in advance for considering to participate in the Fall Forum 2011.</div><div>I look forward to your active participation in this remarkable event.</div><div><br /></div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>Young-Ah Kim</div><div><br /></div><div>English Version: <a href="http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421790016522&amp;e=pdf">http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421790016522&amp;e=pdf</a></div><div>Korean Version: <a href="http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421816055328&amp;e=pdf">http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421816055328&amp;e=pdf</a></div>', '<div style="text-align: center;"><b>Korean Community Fall Forum 2011: Understanding Our Community and Higher Education</b></div><div>I am pleased to invite you to the Korean Community Fall Forum 2011. This is jointly organized by the Toronto Korean Families Study(TKFS) and the Korean-Canadian University Professors Forum(KCUPF).</div><div>This Forum''s aims are threefold: 1)to inform both parents and students who are senior high school or university students about the life of a post-secondary school student; 2)to provide an opportunity for them to meet university professors and current university students for potential networking; 3) it will be the first time t present the results of the TKFS project and to thank publicly the Korean community who supported us.</div><div><br></div><div>Please find details in the attached file. I thank you in advance for considering to participate in the Fall Forum 2011.</div><div>I look forward to your active participation in this remarkable event.</div><div><br></div><div>Sincerely,</div><div>Young-Ah Kim</div><div><br></div><div>English Version: http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421790016522&amp;e=pdf</div><div>Korean Version: http://ksac.ca/download.php?n=1320421816055328&amp;e=pdf</div>', 0, '1325734682');
