(113, '1089634772', 'free', 0, 'Byunghoon Yoon', 'Women Only Craft Night at ACAS!', '<div><img src="http://ksac.ca/upload/1330484294460930.jpg" alt="1330484294460930.jpg" /></div><div><br /></div><div>To celebrate International Women’s Day, ACAS will be hosing an informal discussion on what it means to be women today. A delicious dinner will be served!</div><div>During the night, we will have a craft session. A special guest will teach us how to make bracelets! It will be the perfect opportunity to make a gift for a special woman and/or role model in your life!</div><div><br /></div><div>Craft materials will be provided.</div><div>Free Dinner will be served at 6pm.</div><div>Childcare budget is available, please contact Heywon in advance. </div><div><br /></div><div>R.S.V.P. by March 2nd</div>', '<div><img src="http://ksac.ca/upload/1330484294460930.jpg"></div><div><br></div><div>To celebrate International Women’s Day, ACAS will be hosing an informal discussion on what it means to be women today. A delicious dinner will be served!</div><div>During the night, we will have a craft session. A special guest will teach us how to make bracelets! It will be the perfect opportunity to make a gift for a special woman and/or role model in your life!</div><div><br></div><div>Craft materials will be provided.</div><div>Free Dinner will be served at 6pm.</div><div>Childcare budget is available, please contact Heywon in advance.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>R.S.V.P. by March 2nd</div>', 0, '1330484355'),
