(130, '1089634772', 'announcement', 0, 'Byunghoon Yoon', 'Part-time Job Recruitment in Enteral Nutrition Studies', '<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:center;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">Recruitment in South Korea (Seoul Preferred)</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:center;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">We are currently involved in a study on Enteral Nutrition and Enteral Feeding for patients in and out of the hospital in South Korea (Seoul preferred)</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">We are looking for specialists that are involved in the decision process on the purchase of those materials and are knowledgeable about the different brands and the market trends.</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">This survey is scheduled between <b>2<sup>nd</sup> May and 6<sup>th</sup> May.</b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">Major topics of this survey are: clinical nutrition usage, product usage, disposables, procurement, differences between in and out patients in South Korea.</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><span lang="en-us" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-indent:0cm;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">In particular we would need recruit 7~8 respondents in South Korea (Seoul preferred).</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></b></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;color:rgb(192,0,0);" xml:lang="en-us">Ø<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">4~5 Clinical Nutrition Specialists</span></b></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-indent:0cm;margin-left:21pt;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(192,0,0);font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">(</span><span lang="en-us" style="color:rgb(192,0,0);" xml:lang="en-us">A Clinical Nutrition specialist is a doctor that works in the hospital and typically is not a dietician. It could be a pediatrician, a gastroenterologist. Those specialists generally are also a reference in terms of nutrition for the entire hospital)</span></b></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;" xml:lang="en-us">Ø<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">1  Procurement Director</span></b></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;" xml:lang="en-us">Ø<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">2  ICU head nurses</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><span lang="en-us" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;color:rgb(192,0,0);font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;" xml:lang="en-us">SCREENING CRITERIA for respondents</span></b></p><p style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;" xml:lang="en-us">ü<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">All respondents must have at least a minimum of 3 years of experience in the field of Enteral Nutrition or Enteral feeding in a hospital set .in regardless of working in either government or private hospitals</span></b></p><p align="left" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:left;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">ü<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">All respondents MUST BE involved in the decision process (either influencing or recommending or puchasing or ordering) in the purchase of enteral related products.</span></b></p><p align="left" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:left;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">ü<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">All respondents are knowledgeable about the different brands of enteral products (at least 2 brands or more) and respondents will be asked to provide brand names for the enteral nutrition related brands during the screening stage.</span></b></p><p align="left" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:left;margin-left:21pt;"><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Wingdings;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">ü<span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'';font-size:7pt;">  </span></span><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us">All respondents should be selected out of different hospitals (which means this survey covers 7~8 different hospitals, 1 respondent per hospital), we need to cover at least 2 public hospitals, 2 private hospitals, 2 university hospitals.</span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:10pt;" xml:lang="en-us"> </span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;"><b><span lang="en-us" style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif;" xml:lang="en-us">Job content and Remuneration</span></b></p><p align="left" style